    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required gradation levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped as not-assessed per ASME V&V 40 Table 4 provisions for MRL 2. Validation results demonstrate CFD predictions within 15% of FDA benchmark experimental data across all five operating points, with RH < 1 at worst-case conditions. The 13-factor credibility assessment is complete and supports acceptance of the CFD model for the stated COU.",
